    "client": "MTS",
    "location": "russia",
    "year": 2024,
    "introText": "To represent MTS at the Signal Festival, we designed a set of objects that expand your ability to explore the festival without limits: a set of bandages to keep you moving; a flashlight and a chair to help you find your place anywhere; a crossbody strap to carry everything you need; and a frisbee — to remind you that the most important thing is to have a good time.",
